@startuml OCR_Recognition_Sequence
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

actor User
participant "DocumentCurrency\nActivity" as Activity
participant CameraX
participant "OCRHelper" as OCR
participant "TTSManager" as TTS

User -> Activity: Open Document Reading
Activity -> CameraX: Initialize Camera
CameraX --> Activity: Camera Ready

User -> Activity: Align Document
Activity -> CameraX: Capture Image
CameraX --> Activity: Image Frame

Activity -> OCR: recognizeText(ImageProxy)
activate OCR

OCR -> OCR: Preprocess Image
OCR -> OCR: Run ML Kit OCR
OCR -> OCR: Extract Text Blocks
OCR --> Activity: Recognized Text

deactivate OCR

Activity -> TTS: Read Text Aloud
TTS --> User: Voice Output

alt User Chooses Line-by-Line
    loop For Each Line
        Activity -> TTS: Read Line
        TTS --> User: Line Audio
    end
end

note right of OCR
  Java File:
  OCRHelper.java
  Google ML Kit Text Recognition API
  Supports Chinese & English
end note

@enduml
